abstracts.cdata!:
The Second Technical Assistance Project
            comprises technical assistance in pre-investment planning,
            feasibility and engineering studies, consulting and advisory
            services and training for staff agencies responsible for
            project planning or implementation. Emphasis will be on
            agriculture and water development sectors.
